		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's part of why I asked whether such a pattern was visible on a Nintendo handheld. The GBC, GBA, and DS LCDs darken alternate lines in alternate frames to give a pseudo-interlacing effect that slightly improves pixel response times.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
